title: Sumo Salad
typeOfFood: Lacto, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service salad restaurant chain. Vegans have choice of 5 salads, raisin toast, soups (in winter), fruit salad, and cold pressed juices. Labels which dishes are vegan and cater for a range of dietary requirements, all listed on the menu. Cannot build your own salad as they are pre-made.
